  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sky Jumping</strong> is a challenging first-person platformer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete all the challenges, get to the top and leave your message for future conquerors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.poster.avif?t=1732450824\" width=638 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.webm?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.mp4?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several difficulty levels:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From relatively easy to hardcore without checkpoints.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Difficult jumps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Physical puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tunnel syndrome</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.poster.avif?t=1732450824\" width=638 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.webm?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.mp4?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sky Jumping</strong> is a challenging first-person platformer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete all the challenges, get to the top and leave your message for future conquerors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.poster.avif?t=1732450824\" width=638 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.webm?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/742275bd97b99ab151ed590e9ab55f1d.mp4?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several difficulty levels:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From relatively easy to hardcore without checkpoints.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Difficult jumps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Physical puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tunnel syndrome</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.poster.avif?t=1732450824\" width=638 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.webm?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865660/extras/5ff2e620093051f2c6c7dca7fd7d8c10.mp4?t=1732450824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
